      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner to get it back on the road. The engine is currently non-running and needs a complete overhaul, while the body shows significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a full restoration project.",
